@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2c3e50, #4ca1af);
        color: #fff;
    }

    .card {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border: none;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

    .card-img-top {
        border-top-left-radius: 15px;
        border-top-right-radius: 15px;
        object-fit: cover;
        height: 320px;
    }

    .card-body {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 15px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 15px;
        color: #000;
    }

    .card-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .card-text {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .lead {
        font-weight: 300;
    }

    .content-container {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        color: #000;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

        .content-container h4 {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .content-container p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

    footer {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff416c, #2d96e0);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
    }
</style>

<h1 class="text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="content-container">
    <h4>Meet the Team</h4>
    <p>Behind FoodFrenzy is a passionate team of foodies, tech experts, and customer service professionals dedicated to making your online food ordering experience unforgettable. We work tirelessly to update our database, improve our platform, and provide top-notch customer support to ensure that you have the best possible experience with FoodFrenzy.</p>
    <h4>Our Commitment</h4>
    <p>We are committed to continuously improving and expanding our services to meet the evolving needs of our users. At FoodFrenzy, we value your feedback and are always eager to hear your suggestions on how we can make your online food ordering experience even better.</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing FoodFrenzy as your favourite meal.</p>
</div>
